WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
A quick guide to brewing coffee near the sea.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Use a slightly finer grind; shorten bloom by 10–15 seconds.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
If tap water is chalky, use filtered/bottled ~75–150 ppm as CaCO3.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Rinse filter; preheat brewer; total brew time 2:45–3:15.
